episodes.title: DOJ releases more of the Epstein files, but advocates and victims say it's not enough
episodes.description:
One of Epstein's victims was Virginia Roberts Giuffre. She spoke publicly about the abuse she suffered before she died by suicide earlier this year. Her brother and his family are from Colorado Springs and have been advocating for the release of the files.
